For example, under Windows, execute COLMAP as:

    <KMPKG-ROOT>\packages\colmap_<TRIPLET>\tools\colmap\colmap.exe gui
    <KMPKG-ROOT>\packages\colmap_<TRIPLET>\tools\colmap\colmap.exe mapper
    <KMPKG-ROOT>\packages\colmap_<TRIPLET>\tools\colmap\colmap.exe ...

The package colmap provides CMake integration:

    find_package(COLMAP REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main colmap::colmap)
